full_description:
Lian Li SP750 Performance SFX 80 PLUS Gold Fully Modular Power Supply

The Lian Li SP750 Performance SFX Power Supply is a stylish high-performance PSU that perfectly fits small-form-factor PCs while supporting power-hungry components. It comes with an 80 PLUS Gold Certificate so it can guarantee up to 92% efficiency, ensuring less power wastage. The Lian Li SP750 features a 92mm hydraulic bearing fan that operates at zero RPM mode until 40% load in order to achieve minimal acoustic levels. This PSU features Premium Japanese electrolytic capacitors that provide great durability and long-term reliability, as well as offering the highest stability. This fully modular power supply provides all necessary braided cables right out of the box, ensuring less cable clutter and more aesthetics. It comes with 1 x 24 / 20-Pin motherboard connector (300mm) x 1pcs, 2 x 8 / 4-Pin CPU / ATX 12V connector (450mm-70mm) x 1 pcs, 1 x 8 / 6+2 Pin PCIe connector (400mm) x 1pcs, 2 x 8 / 6+2 Pin PCIe connector (400mm-120mm) x 1pcs, 4 x SATA connector (120mm-120mm-120mm-120mm) x 2pcs, and 4 x 4-Pin Peripheral connector (120mm-120mm-120mm-120mm) x 1pcs. The Lian Li SP750 comes with 5 years of warranty.

full_description:
Lian Li SP850 850W Performance SFX 80 PLUS Gold Fully Modular Power Supply

The Lian Li SP850 850W Fully Modular Power Supply combines looks with high-performance functionality, making it a perfect choice for small-form-factor PCs with power-hungry components. The elegant and timeless design's brushed metal housing lends a touch of sophistication to your system. The SP850 has earned the 80 PLUS GOLD Efficiency certification and delivers an incredible 91.55% efficiency at 115V and 50% load. This level of efficiency decreases power waste, bringing it closer to the 80PLUS PLATINUM standard of 92% efficiency under the same conditions. The Lian Li SP850 stands out for its completely modular construction and braided cables. This not only keeps the inside of your PC clean and nice, but it also allows for easy customization and cable management. The great durability of Japanese electrolytic capacitors improves the reliability and lifetime of the power supply. The SP850 offers a ZERO RPM mode that functions when the load is less than 40% for individuals who desire quiet operation. This function ensures that the power supply remains silent under low-demand scenarios. OVP (Over Voltage Protection), OPP (Over Power Protection), SCP (Short Circuit Protection), UVP (Under Voltage Protection), OCP (Over Current Protection), and OTP (Over Temperature Protection) are all available on the Lian Li SP850. These measures protect both the power source and the connected components from potential hazards. The addition of a 12VHPWR connector cable compatible with 40 series graphic cards enhances the versatility of the PSU, allowing it to meet the needs of modern graphics cards. The Lian Li SP850 is a durable and visually appealing power supply unit that not only meets the power needs of high-performance systems but also adds a touch of class to the overall design. The SP850 blends efficiency, durability, and elegance in a tiny package, making it ideal for PC geeks and gamers alike.
